113
00:06:20,646 --> 00:06:22,341
Now, my first guest tonight...

114
00:06:22,415 --> 00:06:23,575
Well, we in the Nixon camp

115
00:06:23,649 --> 00:06:25,116
really didn't know that much
about David Frost,

116
00:06:25,184 --> 00:06:28,176
other than he was
a British talk show host

117
00:06:28,254 --> 00:06:30,017
with something of
a playboy reputation.

118
00:06:30,089 --> 00:06:33,820
He'd had a talk show
here in the US that
had won some awards

119
00:06:33,893 --> 00:06:38,990
but hadn't syndicated well
and had been dropped
by the network.

120
00:06:39,065 --> 00:06:40,555
He ended up taking
it down to Australia,

121
00:06:40,633 --> 00:06:44,364
which is, I believe,
where he was when
the President resigned.

122
00:06:44,637 --> 00:06:47,128
<i>Next week's guest
will be Evonne Goolagong.</i>

123
00:06:47,206 --> 00:06:49,106
