00:09:43,316 --> 00:09:45,181
Weren't they terrific?

170
00:09:45,251 --> 00:09:49,244
Come on, John,
we've done political
interviews before.

171
00:09:50,523 --> 00:09:53,014
So, okay, so what
kind of interview?

172
00:09:53,092 --> 00:09:58,325
A full, extensive
look-back over his life,
his presidency.

173
00:09:58,397 --> 00:09:59,955
And?

174
