<i>"Truman had his Fair Deal,</i>
<i>now Ford has</i>
<i>his crooked deal. "</i>

204
00:11:30,189 --> 00:11:32,180
<i>There was no deal, period.</i>

205
00:11:32,258 --> 00:11:34,624
<i>I don't think the truth</i>
<i>will ever come out.</i>

206
